snippet.title: KUUKIYOMI 3: Consider It More and More!! - Father to Son - 20 Minute Play [Switch]
snippet.description:
Playing through 20 minutes of KUUKIYOMI 3: Consider It More and More!! on Nintendo Switch. Completing the first 40 scenarios of the game. Then completing a Quick Consider It.

Game: KUUKIYOMI 3: Consider It More and More!!
Platform: Nintendo Switch
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/kuukiyomi-3-consider-it-more-and-more-father-to-son-switch/
Release Date: March 18, 2021
Price: $4.99 ($4.49 launch discount)
